description: If you’re looking for incredible food in Kansas City, Fresh & Tasty Catering can actually bring it straight to you!When planning your next exciting event, just invite this big green truck to roll on up and take care of all your culinary needs. Their wonderfully delicious selection includes favorites like bacon wrapped jalapeños stuffed with savory smoked chicken, plump and juicy pulled pork, oh-so-yummy cheesy scalloped potatoes, and big beautiful sandwiches, like the muffuletta hoagie- stuffed to perfection with honey ham, mortadella, salami, provolone cheese, and flavorful olive salad. Your guests will love all of this and more, and will surely agree that Fresh & Tasty is the absolute best.
name: Fresh & Tasty
